      "[LightGBM] [Warning] No further splits with positive gain, best gain: -inf\n",
      "[LightGBM] [Warning] No further splits with positive gain, best gain: -inf\n",
      "[LightGBM] [Warning] No further splits with positive gain, best gain: -inf\n",
